---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../../components/Header.astro";
import clinkLogo from "../../assets/clink_logo.svg";
---

<Layout title="Clink">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 mt-8">
    <Header />
    <div class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-2">
      <a href="/projects" class="underline decoration-dashed underline-offset-4">← Back to projects</a>
    </div>

    <div class="relative mb-3">
      <img
        src={clinkLogo.src}
        alt="Clink logo"
        class="h-10 md:h-12 object-contain"
        loading="lazy"
      />
      <span
        class="absolute top-0 right-0 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border text-[11px] border-emerald-100 text-emerald-700 bg-emerald-50/70"
      >
        Live
      </span>
    </div>

    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-2">Clink</h1>

    <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4 mb-3 md:w-4/5">
      <div class="text-sm text-gray-800">
        <div class="font-semibold mb-1">In one line</div>
        A digital ledger and debt recovery web application. Streamlines financial tracking and makes managing outstanding balances frictionless.
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2 text-[11px] mb-2">
      <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70">Digital Ledger</span>
      <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70">Debt Recovery</span>
      <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70">React</span>
      <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-emerald-200 text-emerald-700 bg-emerald-50/80">Live</span>
    </div>

    <p class="text-[13px] text-gray-600 mb-4">
      Financial tracking • Debt recovery • React architecture
    </p>

    <p class="text-gray-700 md:w-3/4" style="line-height: 2">
      Clink keeps your numbers honest and your follow-ups clear. It gives you a living record of who owes what, when it was agreed, and how
      balances are being recovered — without messy notebooks or forgotten promises. Issue receipts in seconds, track every cedi, and let Clink
      handle the reminders while you focus on customers.
    </p>

    <section class="mt-6">
      <h3 class="font-semibold mb-3">Built for the informal market</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 md:w-3/4 mb-3" style="line-height: 2">
        Clink is designed for real market life — noisy stalls, low signal, and busy merchants who don't have time to chase debt. Handshake deals
        become digital records: one receipt, one link, one payment. Your notebook becomes a living ledger you can search, trust, and grow with.
      </p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
        <ul class="list-disc ms-5 space-y-1">
          <li>Issue clean, tax‑aware receipts in seconds.</li>
          <li>Track every sale, credit, and repayment.</li>
          <li>See what is owed, by who, and since when.</li>
        </ul>
        <ul class="list-disc ms-5 space-y-1">
          <li>Reminders go out automatically; you keep relationships warm.</li>
          <li>Works with basic phones on the customer side — no app required.</li>
          <li>Simple flows that fit how Ghanaian merchants already sell.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-6">
      <h3 class="font-semibold mb-3">What Clink handles for you</h3>
      <div class="space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
        <p>
          <strong>Works with zero signal:</strong> Clink generates secure, signed QR codes locally on your device. Issue receipts in the deepest
          market basements — we sync to the cloud and send links when you're back online.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>2026 tax‑ready:</strong> We handle the new VAT Act (Act 1151) math so you don't have to. Informal mode gives small traders clean
          receipts (0% VAT); VAT mode breaks out NHIL, GETFund, VAT — ready for your GRA returns.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Clink Credit Passport:</strong> Every on‑time repayment grows your customer's Trust Score. Their phone number becomes a financial
          asset, helping you decide who gets credit and how much.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Automated reminders:</strong> Gentle nudge before due date, clear action on the day, firm notice when overdue. You stay on good
          terms; we keep recovery on track.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-6">
      <h3 class="font-semibold mb-3">Built for Takoradi merchants</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">
        Provisions, electronics, fabrics, hardware — if you sell on credit in Takoradi, Clink is built for you. It also fits freelancers,
        artisans, and service providers who invoice later but still want a clear record and on‑time payments.
      </p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
        <ul class="list-disc ms-5 space-y-1">
          <li><strong>Retailers:</strong> Track small, everyday credits and get paid on time.</li>
          <li><strong>Wholesalers:</strong> Use Trust Scores to decide who gets bigger lines.</li>
          <li><strong>Freelancers &amp; service providers:</strong> Turn verbal agreements into simple digital receipts your clients can pay from.</li>
        </ul>
        <ul class="list-disc ms-5 space-y-1">
          <li><strong>Market traders:</strong> Works with zero signal; signed QR codes generated on your device.</li>
          <li><strong>MoMo users:</strong> Money goes straight from their wallet to yours. Clink doesn't hold funds.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-6">
      <h3 class="font-semibold mb-3">How it works</h3>
      <ol class="list-decimal ms-5 space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-700">
        <li>
          <strong>Generate:</strong> Add the sale in Clink. We generate a signed QR locally on your device. The receipt is the contract; when
          you're back online, we sync and send the link.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Deliver:</strong> Share the link by SMS or WhatsApp, or show a QR. Your customer doesn't need a smartphone app — just a phone
          with a browser.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Pay:</strong> They tap the link and pay with MoMo. You get the money immediately; the ledger and Trust Score update in the
          background.
        </li>
      </ol>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-6">
      <h3 class="font-semibold mb-3">Pricing snapshot</h3>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-zinc-200 bg-white/60 p-3">
          <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-500 mb-1">Starter</div>
          <div class="font-semibold mb-1">Side hustles • GHS 0 / month</div>
          <ul class="list-disc ms-5 space-y-1">
            <li>Free forever.</li>
            <li>50 receipts per month.</li>
            <li>Standard SMS reminders.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50/60 p-3">
          <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-emerald-700 mb-1">Pro — recommended</div>
          <div class="font-semibold mb-1">Active market shops • GHS 25 / month</div>
          <ul class="list-disc ms-5 space-y-1">
            <li>Unlimited receipts & Trust Score lookups.</li>
            <li>WhatsApp + voice nudges.</li>
            <li>Or 1% per recovery, capped at GHS 50.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-zinc-200 bg-white/60 p-3">
          <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-500 mb-1">Enterprise</div>
          <div class="font-semibold mb-1">Distribution centres • GHS 99 / month</div>
          <ul class="list-disc ms-5 space-y-1">
            <li>Bulk issue and advanced controls.</li>
            <li>Trust Score API access.</li>
            <li>Custom legal notices and workflows.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
        Need a one‑off push? Use a <strong>Power Day pass</strong> (GHS 2) for a day of unlimited receipts during clearance sales — no monthly
        commitment.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-6">
      <h3 class="font-semibold mb-3">Trust &amp; safety</h3>
      <div class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-700">
        <p>
          Clink is a ledger, not a bank. Money moves straight from their MoMo wallet to yours — we never hold funds. We focus on the record:
          who owes what, what was agreed, and what has been paid.
        </p>
        <p>
          We track reputation by phone number, not private MoMo data. Your customers own their Trust Score; you use it to see risk before you
          lend, not to replace your own wisdom.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-8 mb-4">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        <a
          href="https://useclink.netlify.app"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-emerald-600 bg-emerald-600 text-white text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-emerald-700 hover:border-emerald-700"
        >
          Visit Clink
        </a>
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70 text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-white"
        >
          Talk about Clink
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>

